hoi calls the shots in the office and at home. Tai-hoi is certain his son Chin Kai-loy is incompetent, so he forces him to make progress by continually putting pressure on him. Although Tai-hoi’s lover Hung Mui-kwai has been hinting all kinds of ideas to him, but Tai-hoi still has not promised to honor her. Tai-hoi’s daughter Chin Yau-fong goes into business while keeping her father in the dark. Tai-hoi slyly undermines her efforts as he feels betrayed. Tai-hoi is kidnapped. And staff member Chiu Yat-ming comes to his rescue. Tai-hoi becomes suspicious of people around him, so he moves into Yat-ming’s home. And he wants Yat-ming to covertly investigate. However, Yat-ming’s father Chiu Chi-yung is astonishingly Yau-fong’s ex-boyfriend, whom Tai-hoi disliked. Tai-hoi always loves money more than anything else. But his way of thinking somehow changes as he gets along with Yat-ming.","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"253322","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2025-01-07T19:10:53.000Z","cast":["Trịnh Tắc Sĩ","Tiêu Chính Nam","Amy Fan","Archie Sin","Tào Vĩnh Liêm","Felix Ng","Phó Gia Lợi","Yuki Law"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Trịnh Tắc Sĩ","name_vi":"Trịnh Tắc Sĩ","name_original":"Kent Cheng Jak-Si","tmdb_id":65966,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a1ebM3aLwYkPckPzc9FgfW2xTsZ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/65966"},{"name":"Tiêu Chính Nam","name_vi":"Tiêu Chính Nam","name_original":"Edwin Siu","tmdb_id":1059226,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bPEjnmBPWTZcrWQklkqcT1bUQwb.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1059226"},{"name":"Amy Fan","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Amy Fan","tmdb_id":1132172,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wvKQcymCS4MaHwpfIdq1CauXij1.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1132172"},{"name":"Archie Sin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Archie Sin","tmdb_id":4687562,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5bLZ2w3mqOvFzK8u2DC29MRgD5K.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://